high_descs: Move around and walk towards the sofa.
Pick up the butterknife from the sofa.
Then turn around and move beside the bread.
Do cut the bread on the sofa using knife.
Again move around and head to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the butterknife inside it beside the joystick, then close it.
Turn left and move to the sofa.
Pick a piece of the bread from the loaf that is cut.
Then turn around and move to the microwave.
Place the bread in the oven by opening it.
Then close the garbagecan and heat the things present in it.
After heating pick the bread piece from the oven and head towards the garbagecan, then pack it.
anns.task_desc: Heat a piece of bread in the oven sliced with knife and pack it in the GarbageCan.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the butterknife from the couch.
Turn around and go near the bread.
Slice the bread into pieces using the knife.
Then go near the microwave.
Put the butterknife into the microwave.
Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the bread from the couch.
Turn around and go near the microwave table.
Put the bread into the oven.
Baked it and take from the oven and go near the garbagecan.
Placed the bread on the garbagecan.
anns.task_desc: Slice the bread using knife and put it in the GarbageCan.

high_descs: Walk to the sofa.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn right to walk to the larger bread.
Slice the bread on the right with the knife.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Put the butterknife in the microwave.
Turn around to reach the larger sofa.
Pick up a slice of bread from the couch.
Turn around and head back to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to walk to the garbagecan on the left of the room.
Put the slice of bread on the garbagecan.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread on the smaller GarbageCan.
